---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TabNav from '../components/TabNav.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Add Dish | Dish Diary">
  <TabNav currentPath={Astro.url.pathname} />
  <section class="card">
    <h2>How to add a new dish</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Create a new markdown file in <code>src/content/dishes/</code> using the template below.</li>
      <li>Add raw image(s) into <code>raw-images/</code> (for example <code>raw-images/mtr/rava-idli.jpg</code>).</li>
      <li>Commit and push. Cloudflare Pages will run image processing and deploy.</li>
    </ol>
    <pre>---
name: "Dish Name"
restaurant: "Restaurant Name"
rating: 4.5
date: 2026-02-13
tags: [tag1, tag2]
image: dish-name
locations:
  - 12.9716,77.5946
  - 12.9823,77.6229
---
Notes about this dish.
    </pre>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
